<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="description" content="中秋诗词鉴赏——千古名篇共赏明月，品读经典感受诗意中秋">
<title>诗词鉴赏 — <%= config.site_title %></title>
<link href="/css/common.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="/css/animations.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="/css/pages.css" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ============================================================
   诗词鉴赏页 — 悬停展开卡片系统
   ============================================================ */

/* ---- 诗词卡片分栏（每列独立，展开仅影响本列） ---- */
.poetry-grid-new {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

/* ---- 独立列容器 ---- */
.poetry-col {
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 20px;
}

/* ---- 单个诗词卡片 ---- */
.poem-card {
  position: relative;
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  border-radius: 14px;
  cursor: pointer;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 20px 18px;
}
.poem-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-glow);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(245,210,122,0.15), 0 0 30px rgba(245,210,122,0.06);
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  z-index: 10;
}

/* ---- 标题（始终可见） ---- */
.poem-card .pc-title {
  font-family: var(--font-title);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: var(--moon-gold);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 1.5;
  transition: all 0.4s ease;
}
.poem-card:hover .pc-title {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
}

/* ---- 作者名（始终可见） ---- */
.poem-card .pc-author {
  font-family: var(--font-poetry);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 4px;
  transition: all 0.4s ease;
}

/* ---- 分隔线（悬停显示） ---- */
.poem-card .pc-divider {
  width: 30px;
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--border-glow);
  margin: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: scaleX(0);
  transition: all 0.4s ease 0.1s;
}
.poem-card:hover .pc-divider {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: scaleX(1);
  margin: 12px 0;
}

/* ---- 诗歌正文（悬停显示） ---- */
.poem-card .pc-body {
  font-family: var(--font-poetry);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  line-height: 2.2;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-align: center;
  max-height: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.5s ease, opacity 0.45s ease 0.15s;
}
.poem-card:hover .pc-body {
  max-height: 500px;
  opacity: 1;
}

/* ---- 朝代标签 ---- */
.poem-card .pc-dynasty-tag {
  position: absolute;
  top: 10px;
  right: 10px;
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15);
  border-radius: 8px;
  opacity: 0.5;
  transition: all 0.4s ease;
}
.poem-card:hover .pc-dynasty-tag {
  opacity: 0.8;
  border-color: rgba(245,210,122,0.3);
  color: var(--moon-gold);
}

/* ---- 响应式 ---- */
@media (max-width: 550px) {
  .poetry-grid-new { max-width: 380px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .poem-card .pc-title { font-size: 1.1rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body data-journey="poetry">

<div class="page-transition active"><div class="moon-loader"></div></div>

<nav class="navbar">
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
    <div class="logo-icon"></div>
    <span>月满中华</span>
  </a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <% nav.forEach(function(item) { %>
      <a href="<%= item.href %>"<%= item.href === '/poetry' ? ' class="active"' : '' %>><%= item.label %></a>
    <% }); %>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-actions">
    <div class="nav-user">
      <% if (user) { %>
        <div class="user-avatar"><%= user.username.charAt(0).toUpperCase() %></div>
        <span class="user-name"><%= user.username %></span>
        <div class="user-dropdown">
          <a href="/logout">退出登录</a>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/login" class="nav-login-btn">登录</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-toggle"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="bg-particles"></div>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="cloud-pattern"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <span class="hero-icon">📜</span>
    <h1>月下华章</h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">诗词鉴赏 · 千古明月</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="page-content">
  <div class="section-title reveal">
    <h2>中秋经典诗词</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">悬停品读佳作 · 点击深入赏析</p>
    <div class="divider"><span class="dot"></span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="poetry-grid-new">

    <!-- 1. 水调歌头 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/shuidiaogetou'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">宋</span>
      <div class="pc-title">水调歌头</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【宋】苏轼</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">明月几时有？把酒问青天。<br>不知天上宫阙，今夕是何年。<br>我欲乘风归去，又恐琼楼玉宇，<br>高处不胜寒。<br>起舞弄清影，何似在人间。<br>……但愿人长久，千里共婵娟。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 2. 望月怀远 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/wangyuehuaiyuan'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">唐</span>
      <div class="pc-title">望月怀远</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【唐】张九龄</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">海上生明月，天涯共此时。<br>情人怨遥夜，竟夕起相思。<br>灭烛怜光满，披衣觉露滋。<br>不堪盈手赠，还寝梦佳期。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 3. 月夜忆舍弟 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/yueyeyishedi'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">唐</span>
      <div class="pc-title">月夜忆舍弟</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【唐】杜甫</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">戍鼓断人行，边秋一雁声。<br>露从今夜白，月是故乡明。<br>有弟皆分散，无家问死生。<br>寄书长不达，况乃未休兵。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 4. 静夜思 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/jingyesi'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">唐</span>
      <div class="pc-title">静夜思</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【唐】李白</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">床前明月光，疑是地上霜。<br>举头望明月，低头思故乡。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 5. 十五夜望月 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/shiwuyewangyue'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">唐</span>
      <div class="pc-title">十五夜望月</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【唐】王建</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">中庭地白树栖鸦，冷露无声湿桂花。<br>今夜月明人尽望，不知秋思落谁家。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 6. 春江花月夜 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/chunjianghuayueye'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">唐</span>
      <div class="pc-title">春江花月夜</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【唐】张若虚</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">春江潮水连海平，海上明月共潮生。<br>滟滟随波千万里，何处春江无月明。<br>江畔何人初见月？江月何年初照人？<br>人生代代无穷已，江月年年望相似。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 7. 中秋月 (晏殊) -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/zhongqiuyue1'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">宋</span>
      <div class="pc-title">中秋月</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【宋】晏殊</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">十轮霜影转庭梧，此夕羁人独向隅。<br>未必素娥无怅恨，玉蟾清冷桂花孤。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 8. 太常引 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/taichangyin'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">宋</span>
      <div class="pc-title">太常引</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【宋】辛弃疾</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">一轮秋影转金波，飞镜又重磨。<br>把酒问姮娥：被白发、欺人奈何？<br>乘风好去，长空万里，直下看山河。<br>斫去桂婆娑，人道是、清光更多。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 9. 八月十五夜玩月 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/bayuewanli'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">唐</span>
      <div class="pc-title">八月十五夜玩月</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【唐】刘禹锡</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">天将今夜月，一遍洗寰瀛。<br>暑退九霄净，秋澄万景清。<br>星辰让光彩，风露发晶英。<br>能变人间世，翛然是玉京。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 10. 中秋 (李朴) -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/zhongqiulipu'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">宋</span>
      <div class="pc-title">中秋</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【宋】李朴</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">皓魄当空宝镜升，云间仙籁寂无声。<br>平分秋色一轮满，长伴云衢千里明。<br>狡兔空从弦外落，妖蟆休向眼前生。<br>灵槎拟约同携手，更待银河彻底清。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 11. 琵琶仙 · 中秋 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/pipaxian'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">清</span>
      <div class="pc-title">琵琶仙 · 中秋</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【清】纳兰性德</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">碧海年年，试问取、冰轮为谁圆缺？<br>吹到一片秋香，清辉了如雪。<br>愁中看、好天良夜，知道尽成悲咽。<br>只影而今，那堪重对，旧时明月。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 12. 一剪梅 · 中秋无月 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/yijianmei'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">宋</span>
      <div class="pc-title">一剪梅 · 中秋无月</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【宋】辛弃疾</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">忆对中秋丹桂丛，花在杯中，月在杯中。<br>今宵楼上一尊同，云湿纱窗，雨湿纱窗。<br>浑欲乘风问化工，路也难通，信也难通。<br>满堂唯有烛花红，歌且从容，杯且从容。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 13. 中秋对月 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/zhongqiuduiyue'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">唐</span>
      <div class="pc-title">中秋对月</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【唐】曹松</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">无云世界秋三五，共看蟾盘上海涯。<br>直到天头天尽处，不曾私照一人家。</div>    </div>

    <!-- 14. 阳关曲 · 中秋月 -->
    <div class="poem-card reveal" onclick="location.href='/poetry/yangguanqu'">
      <span class="pc-dynasty-tag">宋</span>
      <div class="pc-title">阳关曲 · 中秋月</div>
      <div class="pc-author">【宋】苏轼</div>
      <div class="pc-divider"></div>
      <div class="pc-body">暮云收尽溢清寒，银汉无声转玉盘。<br>此生此夜不长好，明月明年何处看。</div>    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-content">
    <div class="footer-links">
      <% nav.forEach(function(item) { %><a href="<%= item.href %>"><%= item.label %></a><% }); %>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-divider"></div>
    <div class="footer-info">
      <p><span class="highlight"><%= config.site_title %></span></p>
      <p><%= config.footer_text %></p>
